description: Street Fusion is serving up gourmet Vietnamese meals to the streets of the Bay Area. Our delicious lettuce wraps, healthy rice bowls, and mouth-watering Banh Mi Sandwiches will have you feeling right & feeling light (on your toes).  All of our food is fresh, organic, and gluten free with non-Gmo ingredients.  Our meals are made-to-order and you will notice the difference; both in the quality & your waist line.  Follow us on social media & come experience Street Fusion for yourself.
name: Street Fusion
